://github.com/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pull/41", "diff_url": "https://github.com/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pull/41.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pull/41.patch", "merged_at": "2025-09-12T19:55:07Z"}, "body": "With this PR, I would like to introduce the possibility to explicitly choose which local IP should be used for sending out email. This is useful if your machine has multiple public IPs assigned, and you want to ensure that you are using the intended one. Using an IP with good repudiation is quite important when you want to ensure deliverability.\r\n\r\nNote that the configuration option is completely optional, and the changes are backward compatible.\r\n\r\nPlease let me know if you have any further questions or would like me to optimize the code in some way.", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send/issues/41/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send/issues/41/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send/issues/33", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send/issues/33/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send/issues/33/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send/issues/33/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pull/33", "id": 2277742577, "node_id": "PR_kwDOHZ46KM5ueh1T", "number": 33, "title": "Derive Clone for mail_send::smtp::message::{Message, Address, Parameters, Parameter}.", "user": {"login": "janis-ab", "id": 137309430, "node_id": "U_kgDOCC8s9g", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/137309430?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab", "html_url": "https://github.com/janis-ab", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janis-ab/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2024-05-03T13:58:34Z", "updated_at": "2024-05-05T14:16:50Z", "closed_at": "2024-05-05T14:16:49Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pulls/33", "html_url": "https://github.com/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pull/33", "diff_url": "https://github.com/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pull/33.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/stalwartlabs/mail-send/pull/33.patch", "merged_at": "2024-05-05T14:16:49Z"}, "body": "At the moment `SmtpClient::send` takes `impl IntoMessage` as an argument, thus it takes ownership of a message and in times when message sending fails and it is necessary to retry sending the same message a bit later, it is not possible to do so, because it has been moved.\r\n\r\nThis is why we #[derive(Clone)] for Message, Address, Parameters, Parameter.\r\n\r\nNow it is possible to clone message before sending it. On success we can drop the original, on retry cases we can clone original again, update some parameters and resend.", "